OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,FThe former oil capital of Europe has a
OL,8,F"genuine opportunity" to redefine
OL,9,Fitself amid the switch from fossil
OL,10,Ffuels to renewables ` but an expert
OL,11,Fhas warned it is "very much entering a
OL,12,Fmake-or-break period".
OL,14,FProfessor Paul de Leeuw, director of
OL,15,Fthe Energy Transition Institute at
OL,16,FAberdeen's Robert Gordon University,
OL,17,Fspoke out as a report warned that up
OL,18,Fto 18,000 jobs could be lost from the
OL,19,Foffshore energy workforce in the
OL,20,Fperiod up to 2035 ` the equivalent of
OL,21,Fabout 1,600 job losses a year.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@UO]sD@ROUtD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,FA report from the Institute said that
OL,8,Fwhile the switch to renewables could
OL,9,Fallow Scotland's north east to
OL,10,Freinvent itself as a "world class,
OL,11,Fmulti-energy hub", it added there is a
OL,12,F"Goldilocks zone" over the next five
OL,13,Fyears, during which the decline in the
OL,14,Foil and gas workforce must be matched
OL,15,Fby growth in the green energy sector
OL,16,Fto prevent a permanent loss of skills
OL,17,Fand jobs.
OL,26,@rD@VOUsD@QO]tD@AOUtD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,FThe north east of Scotland currently
OL,8,Fhas about one in three of the UK's
OL,9,F115,000 offshore oil and gas jobs and
OL,10,Fabout one in four of the 154,000
OL,11,Foffshore energy jobs.
OL,13,FCurrently, about 90% of the regional
OL,14,Foffshore energy workforce is employed
OL,15,Fin oil and gas, with the the remaining
OL,16,F10% in renewables ` but by 2035
OL,17,Fbetween 55% and 70% of the jobs could
OL,18,Fbe in the green energy sector.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,FThe report suggested the north east of
OL,8,FScotland, which has been the base for
OL,9,Fmuch of the North Sea oil and gas
OL,10,Findustry, was "already well
OL,11,Fpositioned" to benefit from renewables.
OL,13,FThat comes as the UK is one of five
OL,14,Fcountries expected to deliver most of
OL,15,FEurope's target of having 300
OL,16,Fgigawatts of installed capacity for
OL,17,Foffshore wind power by 2050, which the
OL,18,Freport says "presents a material
OL,19,Fopportunity for countries bordering
OL,20,Fthe North Sea and, in particular, for
OL,21,Fthe north east of Scotland".
OL,26,@rD@OOUsD@KO]zD@MOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,FProf de Leeuw said: "A picture is now
OL,8,Fclearly developing of how the one-time
OL,9,Foil capital of Europe has a genuine
OL,10,Fopportunity to redefine itself and
OL,11,Freaffirm its status as a global centre
OL,12,Fof energy excellence.
OL,14,F"The workers who helped build one of
OL,15,Fthe world's most productive offshore
OL,16,Fbasins have the skills to power its
OL,17,Fnext chapter.
OL,26,@oD@UOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,F"It should give rise to a sense of
OL,8,Fcautious optimism, but the question is
OL,9,Fwhether the conditions are put in
OL,10,Fplace quickly enough for that to
OL,11,Fhappen."
OL,13,FHe stressed most energy jobs were
OL,14,F"highly transferrable" from oil and
OL,15,Fgas to offshore renewables, adding
OL,16,Fthat workers require "short-term
OL,17,Fupskilling rather than wholesale
OL,18,Fretraining".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@HO]vD@AOUvD@VO]xD@VOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,FThis, the expert added, gives the area
OL,8,F"a structural head start that few
OL,9,Fother regions in the UK or Europe can
OL,10,Fmatch".
OL,12,FHe stressed the need for investment in
OL,13,Frenewables, to keep the jobs in the
OL,14,Fnorth east, with the report warning
OL,15,Fthe next five years would be "a make-
OL,16,For-break period in which the reduction
OL,17,Fof the region's oil and gas workforce
OL,18,Fneeds to be matched by growth in
OL,19,Foffshore renewables employment".
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@FO]wD@^OU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,FProf de Leeuw said: "The Goldilocks
OL,8,Fzone is real and the window is
OL,9,Fclosing. Once that skilled workforce
OL,10,Fdisperses, it does not come back.
OL,12,F"The north east of Scotland has the
OL,13,Fassets, the geography, and the people
OL,14,Fto make this transition work. What it
OL,15,Fneeds now is the investment, policy
OL,16,Falignment, and co-ordination to match.
OL,26,@oD@UOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,F"The real risk is that if experienced
OL,8,Fworkers leave the region before
OL,9,Frenewables can offer comparable
OL,10,Fopportunities, the skills base will
OL,11,Ferode.
OL,13,F"The supply chain capacity would also
OL,14,Freduce, and when offshore wind
OL,15,Fprojects arrive at scale, the
OL,16,Fworkforce to deliver them may no
OL,17,Flonger be here. We are very much
OL,18,Fentering a make-or-break period."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,FUK energy minister Michael Shanks
OL,8,Fsaid: "We aren't turning off the taps
OL,9,Fon oil and gas in the North Sea but we
OL,10,Fare building up the jobs for the
OL,11,Ffuture.
OL,13,F"There are already thousands of jobs
OL,14,Fin renewable energy and upgrading the
OL,15,Fgrid across Scotland, and, as this
OL,16,Freport sets out, oil and gas workers
OL,17,Fare in prime position to take up these
OL,18,Fopportunities.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,F"We are determined to fix what went
OL,8,Fbefore ` a broken transition with a
OL,9,Fworkforce falling by a third over the
OL,10,Fpast decade without the investment in
OL,11,Fwhat comes next. We will protect this
OL,12,Fhighly-skilled workforce now and
OL,13,Fcreate the next generation of good
OL,14,Fjobs across Scotland."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,FScottish energy minister Stephen
OL,8,FGethins said: "The Scottish Government
OL,9,Fis investing to support Scotland's
OL,10,Fvalued and highly skilled energy
OL,11,Fworkforce through the creation of new
OL,12,Fjobs, funded training opportunities to
OL,13,Fpreserve a highly skilled workforce in
OL,14,Fthe North East, and skills development
OL,15,Fto train up the next generation.
OL,26,@pD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,F"This includes #17 million in the
OL,8,Flatest round of our Just Transition
OL,9,FFund, adding to the more than #85
OL,10,Fmillion that has been invested into 28
OL,11,Fprojects across the region since 2022
OL,12,F` helping to support hundreds of jobs
OL,13,Fand companies entering the offshore
OL,14,Fwind, marine energy and carbon capture
OL,15,Fsectors.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,F"However, a just and managed
OL,8,Ftransition for the workforce requires
OL,9,Fa parallel approach, in which North
OL,10,FSea oil and gas production is managed
OL,11,Falongside the increasing deployment of
OL,12,Frenewables. Currently reserved
OL,13,Fpolicies, such as the energy profits
OL,14,Flevy, are driving an accelerated
OL,15,Fdecline of North Sea oil and gas
OL,16,Fbefore renewables can be ready,
OL,17,Fputting that transition at risk.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782181080
OL,3,CNorth-east Scotland approaching
OL,4,C'Goldilocks zone' for energy
OL,5,Ctransition ` expert
OL,7,F"That's why the Scottish Government is
OL,8,Fcalling for North Sea oil and gas
OL,9,Fprojects to be assessed on a case by
OL,10,Fcase basis with climate compatibility
OL,11,Fand energy security as key
OL,12,Fconsiderations, and for the UK
OL,13,FGovernment to replace the energy
OL,14,Fprofits levy with a fair system to
OL,15,Fprotects jobs, energy security and
OL,16,Finvestment in our energy sector."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
